<br>
First off i would like to say is. STFU. Be happy that you even got these skills. It is a big step from SoV and if you cant use a skill doesnt mean anouther person of the same class couldnt. And remember its better than nothing. Hell you could be moping around farming for one of your 100 twinks still.<br>
<br>
Sure some classes got the better of these skill's while some not so great. Ever think that they needed it? Lets look at it some.<br>
<br>
General Skills : Every class gets the same choice. This area is to help out your base stats and the base of your char. Your stats, saves , regen , run speed , how much you eat and how much you breathe and so on. This right here is definetly great. You lacking somthing? fix it. Put some points into int so you can move your armor around to make up for anuother stat you need. General Skills = Uber acknoledge this and work with what you get. Im not here to listen to you cry.<br>
<br>
Arch type skills : this is where things break off int casters , priests , and melee. Hybrids get most of both areas ie an SK for example will get Combat Agility , stability , fury , fear resistance , natural duribility , natural healing (all melee skills) and Chanelling focus , mental clarity, spell casting fury (uber /nod) , deftness , expertise and subteletly (useless for hybrids but eh its an option). Thats alot of chit heh. anyway This is where we hit pay dirt. Arch skills is where your performance starts to get better. Regen more hp , Mana and the list goes on . oh and of course crits. every class can crit with somthing! oh your not critting as much as that person over there and not as hard? think i give a fuck? work your stats improve your gear. All this time your bitching you could be improving yourself.<br>
<br>
Class skills im not going to get into cause that is to much shit to cover. For some it really pays off like rangers. But hey your rangers NEEDED a boost. And my god Mage's and Wizards are godly with spell casting fury. So rogues and BL's didnt get that great of stuff. Ever think rogues were really unbalanced? and maybe this kinda balances shit out. So you dont like your acrobatics , ambidextry and apply poison. well other rogues might who actually know how to do other shit than bs.<br>
<br>
Some classes may have gotten a better deal and probaly needed it. So just remember if you start to bitch and moan about you getting the short end of the stick. Bitch to some one who can actually fucking do somthing about it and WILL. Dont think its a good way to strike up a good convo. I dont even want to hear it.<br>
<br>
